doc.after: Ruthenium forms a variety of coordination complexes Examples are the many pentammine derivatives Ru NH3 5L n which often exist in both Ru II and Ru III Derivatives of bipyridine and terpyridine are numerous best known being the luminescent tris bipyridine ruthenium II chloride
